  "title": "Digestive biscuits",
  "subtitle": "Wholemeal semi-sweet biscuits with a short snap",
  "excerpt": "Digestives are made with a mix of wholemeal and plain flour with a modest amount of butter and sugar. The texture should be dry and slightly crumbly with a clean snap — not soft or chewy. Roll them thin and bake until dry throughout.",
